OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fthis evening with just a few showers
OL,7,Faround. Then the rest of the night
OL,8,Fwill be cloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,9,Fspreading northeast, occasionally
OL,10,Fheavy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FQuite cloudy in the morning
OL,13,Fwith some rain. Variable amounts of
OL,14,Fcloud and sunny spells in the
OL,15,Fafternoon along with scattered slow
OL,16,Fmoving showers, occasionally heavy.
OL,17,FWest coast drier later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
